what_failed:
Regression (0.27x): ** Pre-filtered all three date_dim tables into separate CTEs, then used them to filter the three fact tables individually before joining. This reduces the fact tables early and avoids scanning unfiltered data.

**Expected speedup:** ~2-3x from early reduction of large fact tables via date filters before multi-way joins.
why_it_failed: Pre-filtered and joined store_sales to date CTE BEFORE the 3-way fact table join (store_sales <- store_returns <- catalog_sales). By materializing the date-filtered store_sales early, the optimizer loses the ability to push filters across the multi-way fact join and reorder joins optimally.
